Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.82,0:01:36.95,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}便能化為一抹微笑
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.95,0:01:43.74,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}或許那是悄悄埋下的願望
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.04,0:01:46.75,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}讓奇蹟綻放
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.00,0:01:53.71,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}將那最最重要的寶物找到
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.71,0:02:00.01,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}便是我們此行的目標
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.01,0:02:06.73,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}雖不知能走多遠
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.23,0:02:15.28,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}也要用希望編織當下
